<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عَدِيُّ بْنُ زَيْدٍ:</span> <span class="c2">(البسيط)</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١ - اِلْبَسْ جَدِيدَكَ إِنِّي لابِسٌ خَلَقِي ... وَلا جَدِيدَ لِمَنْ لَمْ يَلْبَسِ الْخَلَقَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
